{"title":"Expressing desire","clock":true,"countdown":0,"intro":{"buttons":{"start":"Start"},"content":[]},"activity":{"scenes":[{"block":"scene","name":"SC1","countdown":0,"instructions":{"open":true,"content":[{"block":"group","class":"flex gap-2 items-center","content":[{"block":"audio","class":"","file":"files/instruccion.mp3","wave":false,"autoplay":false,"id":"","name":"WXz0"},{"block":"text","class":"","text":"Read the infographic to learn about the meaning and use of Would","id":"","name":"3PIZ"}]}]},"content":[{"block":"group","class":"bg-slate-100 rounded p-3 my-2 max-w-5xl mx-auto","content":[{"marker":"","class":"bg-auto h-screen bg-no-repeat p-20 ","content":[{"marker":"","class":"flex justify-center","content":[{"text":"Would","class":"text-center font-bold text-5xl mb-5","id":"4mh7","block":"text","name":"Ln93"}],"background":"","id":"z1Ah","block":"group","name":"cpny"},{"class":"","next":"Next","prev":"Back","content":[{"marker":"","class":"","content":[{"marker":"","class":"","content":[{"text":"I ","class":"","id":"V697","block":"text","name":"IBpt"},{"text":"would ","class":"underline font-bold","id":"7OQS5F1n","block":"text","name":"mOIU"},{"text":"like to have more free time.","class":"","id":"Imz9fchW","block":"text","name":"G3aA"},{"text":"<br>I ","class":"","id":"D1YJq7si","block":"text","name":"9Z7a"},{"text":"wouldn't","class":"underline font-bold","id":"rnkY7wQS","block":"text","name":"jTc3"},{"text":" like to work during the weekend.","class":"","id":"NsrlvnZx","block":"text","name":"VQWL"},{"text":"<br>Would ","class":"underline font-bold","id":"vD8mXWn8","block":"text","name":"YDad"},{"text":"you like to go to the movies?","class":"","id":"PlMtrgmY","block":"text","name":"DO3u"}],"background":"","id":"NdcQ","block":"group","name":"Plcq"},{"marker":"","class":"grid gap-2 mt-5","content":[{"text":"<b>What do these sentences have in common?</b><br>Well, they express desire.","class":"","id":"4VXq","block":"text","name":"T1BD"},{"text":"<b>How are these sentences different?</b>","class":"","id":"EKW4vdmj","block":"text","name":"iS0F"},{"text":"<b>+</b> The first one: ","class":"","id":"w1Wfdbo6","block":"text","name":"hotN"},{"text":"I would like to have more free time.<br>Expresses a desire in affirmative form.","class":"","id":"YYmN9Mcr","block":"text","name":"ymqm"},{"text":"<b>-</b> The second one:","class":"","id":"5NXe3bBX","block":"text","name":"QhJm"},{"text":"I wouldn’t like to work during the weekend.<br>Expresses a desire in a negative form, something we don’t want to happen.","class":"","id":"VjZs1Jhc","block":"text","name":"ZhhL"},{"text":"<b>?</b> The third one:","class":"","id":"L6lkqi5g","block":"text","name":"Txxe"},{"text":"Would you like to go to the movies?<br>This one is a question, so, whenever we want to ask someone about their wishes or desires, we can use  “would” at the beginning of the sentence, in interrogative form.","class":"","id":"2LCejr1g","block":"text","name":"UPr6"}],"background":"","id":"c5OD","block":"group","name":"4Qla"}],"background":"","id":"v1r2","block":"group","name":"nOqn"},{"marker":"","class":"","content":[{"marker":"","class":"","content":[{"text":"I ","class":"","id":"V697qKQA","block":"text","name":"Xg4P"},{"text":"would ","class":"underline font-bold","id":"7OQS5F1njb0R","block":"text","name":"jgzj"},{"text":"like to have more free time.","class":"","id":"Imz9fchWHy6Z","block":"text","name":"TouS"},{"text":"<br>I ","class":"","id":"D1YJq7siVEaU","block":"text","name":"5IM9"},{"text":"wouldn't","class":"underline font-bold","id":"rnkY7wQSflUR","block":"text","name":"V5Z3"},{"text":" like to work during the weekend.","class":"","id":"NsrlvnZxdFjo","block":"text","name":"AISd"},{"text":"<br>Would ","class":"underline font-bold","id":"vD8mXWn8Y3pe","block":"text","name":"G7dy"},{"text":"you like to go to the movies?","class":"","id":"PlMtrgmYKRBN","block":"text","name":"BwyS"}],"background":"","id":"V2KwzOI4","block":"group","name":"Go0X"},{"marker":"","class":"grid gap-2 mt-5","content":[{"text":"Now,  what’s the structure?","class":"","id":"4VXq7yZU","block":"text","name":"GsAb"},{"text":"<b>Affirmative form</b>","class":"","id":"EKW4vdmjf8Ul","block":"text","name":"Xvq5"},{"text":"I would like to go to the movies tonight.<br>Subject + would + like to +verb + the rest","class":"","id":"YYmN9McrFpTh","block":"text","name":"bUih"},{"text":"<b>Negative form:</b>","class":"","id":"5NXe3bBXlgUP","block":"text","name":"at4t"},{"text":"I wouldn’t like to watch a scary movie.<br>Subject + would + not + like to + verb + the rest","class":"","id":"VjZs1Jhc6EaR","block":"text","name":"SYOR"},{"text":"<b>Interrogative form:</b>","class":"","id":"L6lkqi5g6VFW","block":"text","name":"W7Te"},{"text":"Would you like to swim in the ocean?<br>Would + subject + like to + verb + the rest + ?","class":"","id":"2LCejr1gu8f6","block":"text","name":"IgyI"}],"background":"","id":"c5ODG3Jz","block":"group","name":"2F2G"}],"background":"","id":"098xs6C2","block":"group","name":"i7Kc"}],"id":"abBU","block":"slides","name":"ywV6"}],"background":"files/pizarronFondo.png","id":"B2QY","block":"group","name":"5rOx"}],"background":" ","name":"4Cs6","hidden":false,"marker":"","id":""},{"symbol":"FinalizeGroup"}],"id":""}]},"end":{"buttons":{"restart":false},"content":[{"symbol":"finishedAll"}]},"symbols":{"finishedAll":{"class":"w-full","content":[{"block":"group","class":"bg-slate-100 rounded p-5 text-center w-full","content":[{"block":"text","text":"Congratulations, you finished the activity.","class":"","name":"Congra"}],"background":"","name":"CongraGroup"},{"block":"group","class":"text-center p-5","content":[{"block":"finished","name":"finishedBlock"}],"background":"","name":"finishedGroup"}],"background":"","block":"group"},"FinalizeGroup":{"block":"group","class":"text-center mt-10","content":[{"block":"button","class":"mx-auto","to":"/end","text":"Finalize","name":"FinalizeBTN"}],"background":""}}}